txml.parser

Interface XQueryListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    XQueryBaseListener, XQueryInterpreter

    public interface XQueryListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by XQueryParser.
